text: Rais Ali Dilavari Dam is a hydroelectric dam in Iran with an installed electricity generating capability of 70 MW. It is situated in Shabankareh, Bushehr Province.http://en.iwpco.ir/default.aspx ==See also== *Rais Ali Delvari *List of power stations in Iran ==External links== * '''''' ==References== Category:Hydroelectric power stations in Iran Category:Buildings and structures in Bushehr Province
